 founder and CEO) shares the lifelong process of finding lasting career happiness by [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Kristen Wright\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1413:\"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\" wp-image-17023 aligncenter\" alt=\"purposefulpaychecks-featured\" src=\"http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/purposefulpaychecks-featured-417x540.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"486\" /></p>\n<p>Life&#8217;s too short to not love your job! We believe it here at iThemes and we&#8217;re really excited to have just added a new eBook to our Pub Hub, <a href=\"http://ithemes.com/publishing/purposeful-paychecks/\"><em>Purposeful Paychecks: How to Find Lasting Career Happiness</em></a>.</p>\n<p>In this eBook, Cory Miller (iThemes founder and CEO) shares the lifelong process of finding lasting career happiness by outlining <em>6 Principles to Career Happiness</em> and <em>5 Steps to Lasting Career Happiness</em>.</p>\n<h3>6 Principles to Career Happiness</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Living Financially Free</li>\n<li>Seeking Work-Life Alignment</li>\n<li>A Quest for Learning</li>\n<li>Finding Purpose in our Paychecks</li>\n<li>Changing It When It Sucks</li>\n<li>Passing it On</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>5 Steps to Lasting Career Happiness</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Discover what you truly want out of life.</li>\n<li>Search for potential career matches.</li>\n<li>Master the experience and expertise required.</li>\n<li>Hunt relentlessly for the right fit.</li>\n<li>Evaluate and refine as you go</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a class=\"btn blue\" href=\"http://ithemes.com/publishing/purposeful-paychecks/\">Download the PDF</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0