INSERT INTO wp_if_posts VALUES('128', '1', '2011-09-24 00:09:14', '2011-09-24 00:09:14', 'For a minimal fee our trained and experienced cabinetmakers will deliver and install your new furniture in your home, to your satisfaction. For your convenience, deliveries will arrive at your home within a scheduled 4 hour time period. Deliveries are scheduled <em><strong>5 days a week, Tue - Sat.</strong></em>\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, due to liability, we are prohibited to move any of your existing furniture. The area where your new furniture will be placed must be clear of any existing furniture before delivery. Thank you for your cooperation with this matter. If you choose, you may also pick-up your new furniture at the Inspiration warehouse. It is open <span class=\"green\">5 days a week, Tue - Sat.</span> Our helpful staff will quickly and carefully load your furniture into your vehicle for you.\r\n\r\nThe warehouse is located at <span class=\"green\">8380 Chester St., Vancouver, B.C.</span> We are open for pickup <span class=\"green\">Tuesday - Saturday, 9am to 4pm.</span>\r\nYou can reach us at <span class=\"green\">604-730-9484.</span>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"770\" height=\"370\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=8380+Chester+St.,+Vancouver,+B.C.&amp;aq=&amp;sll=53.488046,-122.475586&amp;sspn=19.791579,57.260742&amp;t=h&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=8380+Chester+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V5X+2V3&amp;ll=49.211794,-123.086271&amp;spn=0.010373,0.033002&amp;z=15&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"https://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=8380+Chester+St.,+Vancouver,+B.C.&amp;aq=&amp;sll=53.488046,-122.475586&amp;sspn=19.791579,57.260742&amp;t=h&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=8380+Chester+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V5X+2V3&amp;ll=49.211794,-123.086271&amp;spn=0.010373,0.033002&amp;z=15&a